    <h2
      class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:bottom-[-10px] after:left-1/2 after:transform after:-translate-x-1/2 after:w-20 after:h-1 after:bg-accent">
      ¿Qué aprenderás?
    </h2>

    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16'>
      <div class='bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-t-4 border-primary'>
        <div class='inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary mb-6'>
          <svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'
            ><path d='M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z'></path><polyline points='14 2 14 8 20 8'></polyline><line x1='16' y1='13' x2='8' y2='13'></line><line
              x1='16'
              y1='17'
              x2='8'
              y2='17'></line><polyline points='10 9 9 9 8 9'></polyline></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-medium mb-3 leading-relaxed'>Aprende paso por paso como conciliar la información</h3>
        <p class='text-light-text'>Exógena y minimizar el margen de error en la presentación</p>
      </div>

      <div class='bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-t-4 border-primary'>
        <div class='inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary mb-6'>
          <svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'
            ><path d='M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14'></path><polyline points='22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01'></polyline></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-medium mb-3 leading-relaxed'>Identifica aspectos importantes a la hora de</h3>
        <p class='text-light-text'>Diligenciar cada formato</p>
      </div>

      <div class='bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-t-4 border-primary'>
        <div class='inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary mb-6'>
          <svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'
            ><path
              d='M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z'
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-medium mb-3 leading-relaxed'>Comprende el propósito de cada formato y la información</h3>
        <p class='text-light-text'>Con la que se debe cruzar</p>
      </div>

      <div class='bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg border-t-4 border-primary'>
        <div class='inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary mb-6'>
          <svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'
            ><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle><path d='M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3'></path><line x1='12' y1='17' x2='12.01' y2='17'></line></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class='text-xl font-medium mb-3 leading-relaxed'>Comparte tus dudas con nuestro invitado experto en</h3>
        <p class='text-light-text'>Tributación</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md'>
      <blockquote class='italic text-light-text leading-relaxed relative pl-6 mb-6'>
        “…No se trata de llenar formatos por llenarlos, hay que tener claro cuál es el propósito de la información en el formato, cual es el origen o la fuente de la información y lo que se debe o no
        se debe reportar, antes de iniciar ya debo saber a dónde debo llegar…”
      </blockquote>
      <div class='flex items-center gap-4'>
        <img src='/public/[event]Exogena2024/assets/arlex-pineda-4x4.jpeg' alt='Speaker' class='w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover' />
        <div>
          <p class='font-semibold text-primary'>Arlex Pineda Ocampo</p>
          <p class='text-sm text-light-text'>CEO & Founder Areda SAS</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

